source.name: COMPETE Coallition Members
source.description: This is the list of official members of the COMPETE coalition. The COMPETE coalition is more than 500 electricity stakeholders, including customers, suppliers, generators, transmission owners, trade associations, environmental organizations and economic development corporations - all of whom supprt well-structured competitive electricity markets for the benefit of our country. These companies and customers are spread out over the electricity utility deregulated market in states like Texas, Maryland, Pennsylvania, New Jersey, Connecticut, Illinois, and New York.
